Recalling the decision of the Second Review Conference of the States Parties to the Convention on Prohibitions or Restrictions on the Use of Certain Conventional Weapons Which May Be Deemed to Be Excessively Injurious or to Have Indiscriminate Effects to establish an open - ended group of governmental experts with two separate coordinators on explosive remnants of war and on mines other than anti - personnel mines , See CCW / CONF . II / 2 and Corr . 1 , part II .
