 Leste , Togo , Tonga , Trinidad and Tobago , Tunisia , Turkey , Tuvalu , Uganda , Ukraine , United Arab Emirates , United Republic of Tanzania , Uruguay , Vanuatu , Venezuela ( Bolivarian Republic of ) , Viet Nam , Yemen , Zambia , Zimbabwe
