f Macedonia , Timor - Leste , Togo , Tonga , Trinidad and Tobago , Tunisia , Turkey , Turkmenistan , Tuvalu , Ukraine , United Arab Emirates , United Kingdom of Great Britain and Northern Ireland , United Republic of Tanzania , Uruguay , Uzbekistan , Vanuatu , Venezuela ( Bolivarian Republic of ) , Viet Nam , Yemen , Zambia , Zimbabwe
